posts.name: Jacob
posts.cooked:
Hi!

This year, I am new to programming and FRC. I am currently working on the autonomous code for our bot and have made some simple driving/turning commands. I have the Scheduler.getInstance().run() in my periodic and have an initialization and start of commands in my autonomous initialize. However, when I go into driver station to enable autonomous the robot is stationary. Below, I have attached my code. Could anyone give it a quick glance and let me know what you think is going on.

Thank you so much for your time! Have a great day!
